d":"ebe0c7d65e3bbad0aef9dc23b3b970dec272f44a","tid":1161202,"uid":229883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:33:25.000Z","msg":"心理醫生"},{"pid":"124a360fad8304b39f3e15b26895fbf720063450","tid":1161202,"uid":59465,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"自殘其實係心理壓力大嘅人自我療癒嘅一種方法<br />\n不過當然唔係一個好方法啦<br />\n<br />\n個原理係心理同精神受到傷害嘅時候<br />\n個人唔會知自己幾時好返<br />\n因為心痛係無傷口<br />\n但係肉體嘅傷口就會一日一日咁睇住佢埋口好返<br />\n<br />\n係依個過程入面<br />\n會令到自殘者覺得自己嘅心理問題都一齊好轉<br />\n不過當然係假像嚟<br />\n下次又有其他問題個時又會再自殘<br />\n<br />\n所以巴打你應該多啲關心下佢 陪佢多啲<br />\n問清楚佢到底有咩唔開心<br />\n不過佢唔肯講就唔好逼佢講 太強硬又要增加佢嘅壓力<br />\n最緊要係多啲陪伴佢 有時靜靜地坐係身邊<br />\n已經畀到好多力量對方"},{"pid":"f8b44b6a5cc8de49be1a278fc6c9cb728736ac80","tid":1161202,"uid":160261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:37:23.000Z","msg":"叫佢試下去piercing<br />\n好多時係想用physical pain去numb 咗心理上既痛<br />\n將自己既attention轉移咗去physical pain度"},{"pid":"5e271c5dc8344ed15ce10ff75f2f8f9626d72142","tid":1161202,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:50:09.000Z","msg":"Hints : 殘比邊個睇"},{"pid":"e57dd2ca836a70f1d720d4222ee2f56eead8c1f7","tid":1161202,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"感謝各位Ching<br />\n連登有愛"},{"pid":"325f8eee9e76c77a865a0094c04dd97c6a37ae0f","tid":1161202,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"佢自殘一次你就兜巴車埋去獎勵佢 等佢快啲見耶穌"},{"pid":"e3159bc5517d85d4074a32531f59b684d7055a33","tid":1161202,"uid":192078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c599d9710d1c68313dfef1ad6f63582c2d46643a","tid":1161202,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ff8bb4677cd87c3da8fccedd53fd43e474f3b34","tid":1161202,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6f5f0d1d9ea5f591f9218ea6751dffdf1fbc67c3","tid":1161202,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2